locations.title: New California communities
locations.extract: New California is one of the largest and most well-developed regions of the post-nuclear United States in the Fallout series. This page aims to provide a coherent overview of the communities in the wasteland and roles they play. Note that while these communities reside within the loosely defined boundaries of the territory, not all have been confirmed to date as being an official member of the New California Republic.

factions.title: Punk culture
factions.extract: Punk culture has been referenced throughout the Fallout series, either as real-world inspiration for various story elements and design choices, or in-universe mentions of punk culture in the United States, before and after the Great War.

creatures.title: Aliens
creatures.extract:
Aliens are extraterrestrial creatures from unknown planets.
This article serves as an overview of all alien appearances across the Fallout series. For the most prominent alien species, see Zetans.
